## Forward Process (Noise Scheduling)

Studied how a clean image is gradually converted into random Gaussian noise.

Formula:

xt = √αt · x₀ + √(1 − αt) · ε

Where:

- x₀ = Original Image
- xt = Noisy Image
- ε = Gaussian Noise
- αt = Noise Schedule

---

